[Agent 47 Doesn't Try To Hide Pistols/Items Around NPC's]
author=47iscool
description=This Code Stops Him From Moving Whatever Is In His Right Hand
When Somebody Is Near Him. This One Of Those Annoying
Features That Was Added To This Game And It Does No Good
Because NPC's Can See Your Weapon Even When 47 Attempts
To Hide It, Unless You're Using The Invisibility Code
patch=1,EE,20327D60,extended,00000000

