[Walk Through Walls (ASMv3) (R2+Up On/R2+Down Off)]
author=47iscool
description=This is in fact the last update, it removes un-needed lines of code.
Why another update to remove lines of code you may ask?
Well, the code that was removed was a code that allows Mr. 47 to walk on air.
Don't fret just yet, as there is already a code in place that can set gravity
to it's normal level or just stop it completely. It also will allow him to walk on air just
as with the other code. I have tested this code on real PS2 hardware and it performs
just the same as it did before, only it takes up slightly less space. And the more
free space, the better.
Also the code that was removed can't be used alone, although it does allow
him to walk on air, he can't walk certain ways as it creates invisible walls
in some areas. Here is the code that was removed in case anyone wants it:
>2034FA8C 00000000<
